<li><strong>Set stop-loss orders:</strong> Determine a threshold at which you&#8217;ll exit a trade if the price moves against you. This helps limit your potential losses.</li>



<li><strong>Monitor market conditions: </strong>Stay up-to-date with the latest news and developments in the Binance Coin market to better understand potential risks and opportunities.</li>



